WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:35.719
The remaining nine

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:38.920
are governed by your men.

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:03.040
No one's spoken to me like that

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:05.120
in quite some time.

00:02:08.159 --> 00:02:09.439
Pardon my frankness, my lord.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.199
When a man

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:13.879
has just cheated death,

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:15.479
he finds

00:02:16.520 --> 00:02:18.360
he has very little left to fear.

00:02:31.599 --> 00:02:33.000
Did you imagine

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:35.319
those words would

00:02:35.319 --> 00:02:37.039
cost you your life?

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:40.919
No.

00:02:41.319 --> 00:02:43.000
Quite the opposite.

00:02:44.599 --> 00:02:46.199
You have served me well.

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:50.360
I value a man who

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.680
tells me

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:54.240
what I don't

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:55.800
want to hear.

00:02:56.439 --> 00:02:57.080
You're

00:02:57.439 --> 00:03:00.120
exactly the kind of voice I need.

00:03:01.439 --> 00:03:02.159
Truly!

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:07.759
Now get well.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:08.719
The reforms

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:10.240
are underway.

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:11.800
The empire needs you.

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:13.879
So do I.

00:03:14.919 --> 00:03:15.840
His Majesty has ordered

00:03:15.919 --> 00:03:18.199
a full inquiry into the case.

00:03:19.039 --> 00:03:20.319
Should Wang Xuanfan

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:22.159
prove to be the hand behind it,

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:24.039
no office, however high,

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:28.159
shall bring him to justice.

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.039
Gratitude, my lord.

00:03:32.039 --> 00:03:33.360
See that you rest.

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:35.680
I shall take my leave.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.000
Safe travels, my lord.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.080
I saw

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:03.759
Lord Fu leave just now.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.319
His expression was grim.

00:04:06.199 --> 00:04:07.280
Was there discord between you?

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:09.919
He bade me

00:04:09.919 --> 00:04:11.680
put aside my grudge against Wang.

00:04:12.039 --> 00:04:13.560
I refused him plainly.

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:15.120
I had thought

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:18.920
he might intercede on Wang's behalf,

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:20.360
yet I did not foresee,

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.279
he would shield him

00:04:23.279 --> 00:04:24.720
to such a degree.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:28.839
I told him plainly:

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.600
six of the regions

00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:32.839
where corruption took root

00:04:32.879 --> 00:04:34.319
are governed by Wang's men.

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:36.839
His reply? Merely that they had

00:04:37.399 --> 00:04:38.920
"gone a little too far."

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.360
It beggars belief.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.000
Was that

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:46.680
truly worth

00:04:47.439 --> 00:04:48.959
the confrontation?

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:52.240
I had to test how far

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.120
he would shield Wang.

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.680
And the test has yielded

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:00.000
its answer.

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.000
His bonds with Wang run deeper

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:05.160
than I ever reckoned.

00:05:07.079 --> 00:05:08.160
Then we must

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:10.560
remain vigilant from now on.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:13.680
Not only your affairs at court,

00:05:14.519 --> 00:05:15.600
but my dealings as well.

00:05:16.399 --> 00:05:16.920
Nothing can be

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:18.160
left to chance.

00:05:19.879 --> 00:05:21.439
I should send word

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.120
to Grandmother

00:05:23.399 --> 00:05:24.600
and Yao at once.

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:32.959
Perhaps

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.360
we should return to Tongzhou.

00:05:45.439 --> 00:05:47.720
Ungrateful cur!

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:50.399
He dares rebuke me to my face!

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:53.680
He'd lay the blame for those breaches

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:55.040
at my feet!

00:05:55.439 --> 00:05:56.439
Such insolent words!

00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:57.600
Has he forgotten his place?

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:58.759
It was a threat.

00:06:00.040 --> 00:06:01.600
If I do not remove Wang,

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.560
he will unleash an investigation.

00:06:03.839 --> 00:06:04.319
And when he does,

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:05.519
it won't just be Wang who falls.

00:06:06.199 --> 00:06:07.720
Half the court gets buried.

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:09.519
My lord, please...

00:06:19.399 --> 00:06:20.920
He holds the purse strings.

00:06:22.399 --> 00:06:23.800
Should he choose open war,

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:28.040
I have no means to stop him.

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:32.279
Zhang Qi!

00:06:36.519 --> 00:06:37.800
Lord Fu asks that

00:06:38.319 --> 00:06:40.759
you withdraw for now.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:42.759
Return home and lay low.

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:44.759
When the storm has passed,

00:06:44.959 --> 00:06:45.959
we shall arrange your return.

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:54.600
If that is
Lord Fu's wish,

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.360
I shall comply.

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:29.680
Mind your step.

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:37.519
So many crates.

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.480
What's

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:40.519
inside?

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:42.160
Records from

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:43.720
the bureau,

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:45.519
though they date back ten years now.

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:47.639
When Prince Chengqing rebelled,

00:07:48.319 --> 00:07:49.800
he sought leverage over the officials.

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:51.319
So he bribed his way

00:07:51.519 --> 00:07:52.120
into the bureau

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:53.399
and had every record of conduct

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:54.600
seized and shipped away.

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:56.399
The Cabinet had pirates

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:58.160
seize the convoy.

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:00.639
I managed to move

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:01.720
everything here.

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:04.000
Can records so old

00:08:04.319 --> 00:08:05.519
still serve any purpose?

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:06.600
They can.

00:08:07.839 --> 00:08:09.439
A man's deeds

00:08:09.959 --> 00:08:11.199
always leave traces behind.

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.240
When Lord Fu

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:20.959
entered the Cabinet,

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:22.319
he was

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:24.480
an idealist.

00:08:25.319 --> 00:08:25.920
But

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:27.800
these files

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:28.439
taught me

00:08:29.399 --> 00:08:30.319
something else about him:

00:08:30.759 --> 00:08:31.920
he prizes results

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:34.399
over integrity.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.120
Why is it

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.759
scarcely half full?

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:41.080
I've read all of Lord Fu's records

00:08:41.759 --> 00:08:43.279
and retained what I require.

00:08:44.360 --> 00:08:46.080
I presume you've studied

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.320
Wang's files as well?

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.279
Not a single minister of note

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:50.519
has been left untouched.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.519
How do you intend to proceed?

00:08:58.840 --> 00:08:59.559
Whatever Wang

00:08:59.559 --> 00:09:01.519
holds over Lord Fu

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.320
must be truly damning.

00:09:03.399 --> 00:09:04.440
Nothing less could drive him

00:09:04.759 --> 00:09:05.519
to protect Wang this far.

00:09:07.759 --> 00:09:08.759
Treason?

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:11.159
Could Lord Fu have been in league

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.240
with Prince Chengqing?

00:09:13.679 --> 00:09:14.559
It's possible.

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:17.559
But everything here

00:09:18.039 --> 00:09:19.320
only covers Prince Glorian.

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:30.279
I studied

00:09:30.279 --> 00:09:31.720
his records

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.000
before I dealt with

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.000
his heir.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:36.639
Right about here.

00:09:39.919 --> 00:09:40.399
There.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:50.879
Jingning Era, Year twenty fourth,

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:53.679
Li Zhi summoned the Soulguide Liu Heng

00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:56.279
to pray for his late mother.

00:09:56.799 --> 00:09:58.639
In attendance were

00:09:58.799 --> 00:10:00.159
Zhou Feng,

00:10:00.279 --> 00:10:01.519
steward to Prince Chengqing,

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:02.799
and Wang Nianen, steward to Wang Xuanfan.

00:10:03.759 --> 00:10:05.159
Afterward,

00:10:05.159 --> 00:10:06.919
Wang Nianen sent prayer beads,

00:10:07.679 --> 00:10:09.799
tangerines, pears

00:10:11.039 --> 00:10:13.120
to the residence of

00:10:14.559 --> 00:10:15.840
Grand Secretariat Fu Hailian.

00:10:18.879 --> 00:10:20.000
Who is

00:10:20.159 --> 00:10:21.080
Liu Heng?

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:31.919
Have you heard of

00:10:32.879 --> 00:10:33.879
the Chunyuan Sect?

00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:22.399
Someone cast a stone
over the wall.

00:11:23.759 --> 00:11:24.879
This spell was tied to it.

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:44.559
You think it's Wang Xuanfan?

00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:49.279
Who else would it be?

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:51.039
He's getting reckless!

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:56.000
Men with power

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:57.879
rarely let go of it gracefully.

00:11:58.799 --> 00:12:00.360
My lord, my lady,

00:12:01.159 --> 00:12:02.639
word has come from the palace.

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:05.519
His Majesty has summoned Ye Xian

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:07.240
to lead the investigation

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:08.960
into Chen Yanyun's assassination.

00:12:10.159 --> 00:12:10.759
My lord,

00:12:11.519 --> 00:12:12.519
Ye Xian has never

00:12:12.840 --> 00:12:14.039
shown us any goodwill.

00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:34.519
[By His Majesty's decree:]

00:12:34.519 --> 00:12:36.120
[the investigation into]

00:12:36.200 --> 00:12:38.039
[the assault upon Lord Chen]

00:12:38.039 --> 00:12:39.960
[is now entrusted to Ye Xian.]

00:12:40.159 --> 00:12:42.519
[Ye Xian is to return]

00:12:42.559 --> 00:12:43.759
[to the capital forthwith.]

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.200
Faster!

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:46.559
Valuables are

00:12:46.559 --> 00:12:47.320
to be packed separately!

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:48.960
Mind the fragile pieces!

00:12:52.519 --> 00:12:53.159
Careful!
Stop dawdling!

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:55.039
- You brought this on us!
- Faster!

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.080
You and your obsession

00:12:56.080 --> 00:12:57.240
with destroying

00:12:57.399 --> 00:12:59.000
Chen Yanyun!

00:13:04.039 --> 00:13:05.919
Say something!

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:09.519
This has nothing to do with us...

00:13:09.519 --> 00:13:10.679
Have you quite finished?

00:13:10.879 --> 00:13:12.039
Don't you raise your voice at me!

00:13:12.039 --> 00:13:12.919
You want to
blame someone?

00:13:13.879 --> 00:13:14.720
Blame yourself!

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:15.799
Take your rage out on someone else!

00:13:15.799 --> 00:13:16.559
Hold your tongue!

00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:18.840
Good heavens!

00:14:51.519 --> 00:14:52.360
What did you find?

00:14:55.519 --> 00:14:56.120
Hey!

00:14:56.919 --> 00:14:58.080
What's that for?

00:15:00.639 --> 00:15:01.919
So the wound is real after all.

00:15:02.519 --> 00:15:02.960
It's nothing.
Thought you might be

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:04.720
faking it.

00:15:06.679 --> 00:15:07.360
Enough.

00:15:10.919 --> 00:15:11.720
Tell me,

00:15:12.519 --> 00:15:13.360
how many are dead?

00:15:14.240 --> 00:15:14.840
Three.

00:15:15.519 --> 00:15:16.720
The Wangs,

00:15:17.159 --> 00:15:18.279
and their steward.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:22.519
Wang Nianen?

00:15:23.960 --> 00:15:24.679
How did you know?

00:15:29.279 --> 00:15:30.240
Take me there.

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:43.720
The Wangs

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:45.159
succumbed to charcoal fumes.

00:15:45.320 --> 00:15:46.279
But the steward

00:15:46.279 --> 00:15:47.360
was strangled.

00:15:47.879 --> 00:15:48.320
He clearly

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:50.000
fought for his life.

00:15:50.799 --> 00:15:52.120
They all died

00:15:52.159 --> 00:15:52.879
between

00:15:52.879 --> 00:15:54.440
midnight and dawn.

00:16:02.159 --> 00:16:03.519
Any clues

00:16:04.159 --> 00:16:05.200
on the steward?

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:07.279
Your intuition is keen, my lord.

00:16:07.639 --> 00:16:08.200
Behold.

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:17.200
The steward caused

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:19.120
the Wangs' suffocation.

00:16:20.080 --> 00:16:21.399
Yet, he himself

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:23.120
was murdered.

00:16:24.679 --> 00:16:25.840
Any other findings?

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:34.200
Why is there

00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:35.960
a cut?

00:16:36.559 --> 00:16:37.320
My lady,

00:16:37.840 --> 00:16:38.799
this appears

00:16:39.039 --> 00:16:40.720
to be a nail scratch

00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:42.679
from his own thumb.

00:16:43.600 --> 00:16:45.200
How odd…

00:16:45.600 --> 00:16:47.200
Why would he scratch himself?

00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:48.559
And

00:16:48.879 --> 00:16:49.879
in that exact spot, of all places?

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:02.919
Now I recall…

00:17:04.039 --> 00:17:04.599
He was found

00:17:04.599 --> 00:17:05.759
sitting on the ground

00:17:06.279 --> 00:17:07.160
with his left hand

00:17:08.039 --> 00:17:09.519
clenched in

00:17:10.039 --> 00:17:11.039
a rather peculiar pose.

00:17:11.759 --> 00:17:12.839
Moving the body

00:17:13.200 --> 00:17:14.279
must have disturbed it.

00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:16.519
Can you replicate the pose?

00:17:18.119 --> 00:17:19.279
It was...

00:17:20.559 --> 00:17:21.160
sort of like this.

00:17:28.599 --> 00:17:29.440
The Chunyuan Sect!

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:32.240
The Chunyuan Sect...

00:17:36.039 --> 00:17:37.200
Have you searched

00:17:37.200 --> 00:17:38.200
the entire estate?

00:17:40.279 --> 00:17:41.720
Every corner.

00:17:42.400 --> 00:17:43.400
You have a lead?

00:17:44.119 --> 00:17:45.200
I suspect as much.

00:17:46.400 --> 00:17:47.759
But I need to

00:17:51.519 --> 00:17:52.880
prove it.

00:17:55.559 --> 00:17:57.319
Lord Chen attacked,

00:17:57.319 --> 00:17:58.559
the Wangs dead

00:17:58.559 --> 00:17:59.559
in their own manor!

00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:02.079
These men were the pillars of my throne.

00:18:02.759 --> 00:18:04.039
Has the capital

00:18:04.039 --> 00:18:05.200
fallen into such chaos?

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:06.079
Your Majesty,

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:09.119
it's more than a failure of law.

00:18:09.319 --> 00:18:10.119
Continue, my lord.

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:12.119
Lord Wang

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:13.880
was my aide

00:18:14.119 --> 00:18:15.799
for years;

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:16.920
Yanyun

00:18:17.839 --> 00:18:19.319
is my protégé.

00:18:20.200 --> 00:18:21.400
The mystery

00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:22.920
runs deep,

00:18:23.400 --> 00:18:25.079
and many fear to tread here.

00:18:25.079 --> 00:18:26.119
Let me

00:18:27.039 --> 00:18:28.319
take up this burden myself.

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:41.079
Lord Wang!

00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:44.359
My lord?

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:47.519
You uncovered that

00:18:47.759 --> 00:18:49.319
Wang Xuanfan had

00:18:49.319 --> 00:18:50.799
Chen Yanyun shadowed,

00:18:51.519 --> 00:18:52.240
correct?

00:18:52.480 --> 00:18:53.640
Yes, my lord.

00:18:54.839 --> 00:18:55.880
The man confessed that

00:18:56.319 --> 00:18:58.559
Wang feared Chen would

00:18:58.720 --> 00:18:59.480
expose his ties

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:01.039
to Prince Chengqing.

00:19:01.279 --> 00:19:02.960
He was ordered

00:19:03.200 --> 00:19:04.200
to monitor

00:19:04.319 --> 00:19:05.240
Chen's every move.

00:19:06.119 --> 00:19:08.240
Did you interrogate Wang yourself?

00:19:08.519 --> 00:19:09.759
He was defiant

00:19:10.039 --> 00:19:11.119
and refused to see me.

00:19:11.680 --> 00:19:12.680
Speak your mind,

00:19:12.920 --> 00:19:13.680
my lord.

00:19:14.519 --> 00:19:15.519
I believe

00:19:16.319 --> 00:19:18.880
these two incidents

00:19:18.880 --> 00:19:20.720
are connected.

00:19:20.880 --> 00:19:23.440
They are one and the same!

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:25.640
If Wang truly

00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:27.880
sought Chen's life,

00:19:27.880 --> 00:19:29.680
then who has

00:19:29.680 --> 00:19:30.359
a greater motive

00:19:32.039 --> 00:19:34.000
for revenge

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:36.119
than Chen

00:19:37.519 --> 00:19:38.880
himself?

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:42.720
Unthinkable...

00:19:43.519 --> 00:19:44.200
It has the ring of truth...

00:19:44.519 --> 00:19:45.359
A treacherous turn...

00:19:45.799 --> 00:19:46.319
Aye.

00:19:47.079 --> 00:19:48.039
Your Majesty,

00:19:48.519 --> 00:19:49.920
for an ordinary man

00:19:50.119 --> 00:19:51.640
to slay Wang

00:19:51.799 --> 00:19:53.559
would be a feat of gods.

00:19:53.880 --> 00:19:55.960
But Chen holds prestige rank

00:19:56.240 --> 00:19:57.559
and dark,

00:19:57.880 --> 00:19:59.000
deadly skills.

00:19:59.599 --> 00:20:00.759
The suspicion points

00:20:01.119 --> 00:20:02.960
solely at him!

00:20:03.359 --> 00:20:04.680
This crime is a stain upon us all.

00:20:05.759 --> 00:20:07.160
Your Majesty,

00:20:07.279 --> 00:20:08.720
let justice be

00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:10.039
swift and merciless!

00:20:17.079 --> 00:20:19.440
We implore Your Majesty,

00:20:19.839 --> 00:20:22.400
justice for

00:20:22.400 --> 00:20:24.079
the fallen!

00:20:24.079 --> 00:20:24.599
I...
Your Majesty,

00:20:25.920 --> 00:20:26.839
I implore you.

00:20:27.319 --> 00:20:28.799
Order his arrest at once.

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:30.440
To purge the rot

00:20:30.799 --> 00:20:33.240
from the court.

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:26.880
Lord Chen has arrived!

00:21:51.599 --> 00:21:52.240
Greetings,

00:21:52.920 --> 00:21:53.960
Your Majesty!

00:21:55.559 --> 00:21:56.440
Rise, my lord.

00:21:58.960 --> 00:21:59.880
Gratitude.

00:22:01.359 --> 00:22:02.160
Ought you

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:03.680
not be abed at home?

00:22:04.039 --> 00:22:05.000
Why have you come?

00:22:06.119 --> 00:22:06.839
Your Majesty,

00:22:08.319 --> 00:22:09.400
the tragedy

00:22:10.519 --> 00:22:12.279
of the Wangs reached me.

00:22:12.680 --> 00:22:13.519
I felt

00:22:14.039 --> 00:22:15.240
compelled to attend.

00:22:16.039 --> 00:22:16.839
I'd hate

00:22:17.319 --> 00:22:18.079
for a knife

00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:20.200
to be stuck

00:22:20.759 --> 00:22:22.160
in my back.

00:22:25.400 --> 00:22:27.000
The nerve of the man...

00:22:27.440 --> 00:22:28.559
No shame, truly...

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:32.759
Spare us

00:22:32.759 --> 00:22:35.240
your barbs, my lord.

00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:37.799
I am merely curious,

00:22:38.799 --> 00:22:40.839
you were

00:22:40.839 --> 00:22:41.880
gravely wounded,

00:22:42.319 --> 00:22:43.599
yet you stand before us

00:22:43.839 --> 00:22:44.920
looking quite hale.

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:47.759
You visited my estate

00:22:47.759 --> 00:22:48.880
just days ago,

00:22:49.039 --> 00:22:49.759
offering

00:22:50.119 --> 00:22:51.880
prayers

00:22:52.640 --> 00:22:53.640
for my recovery.

00:22:55.119 --> 00:22:55.680
Now that

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:57.599
I am mending,

00:22:58.079 --> 00:22:58.920
you seem… disappointed?

00:23:00.279 --> 00:23:02.440
I merely raised a reasonable doubt.

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:05.240
No need for such cutting remarks.

00:23:06.079 --> 00:23:06.920
A doubt?

00:23:07.319 --> 00:23:09.000
Or an accusation against Lord Fu?

00:23:10.319 --> 00:23:11.079
My lord,

00:23:11.319 --> 00:23:12.799
you brought a royal healer

00:23:12.799 --> 00:23:13.720
to attend to my wounds.

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:15.640
Is Lord Su disputing

00:23:15.640 --> 00:23:16.799
the healer's findings,

00:23:16.799 --> 00:23:18.000
or your own, my lord?

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:19.000
I... but...
Enough.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:21.000
Cease this

00:23:21.519 --> 00:23:22.920
petty bickering.

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:27.519
Yanyun,

00:23:29.279 --> 00:23:31.119
the Wangs are dead.

00:23:31.920 --> 00:23:32.720
Suspicion

00:23:33.200 --> 00:23:34.319
trails you.

00:23:34.799 --> 00:23:35.799
You must

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:37.359
submit

00:23:37.839 --> 00:23:39.440
to an inquiry.

00:23:40.200 --> 00:23:40.759
How so,

00:23:41.359 --> 00:23:42.640
my lord?

00:23:43.119 --> 00:23:45.319
You told me yourself that

00:23:45.799 --> 00:23:46.599
you

00:23:47.039 --> 00:23:48.359
lacked proof of

00:23:48.359 --> 00:23:49.319
Wang's collusion

00:23:49.519 --> 00:23:50.680
with Prince Chengqing.

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:52.400
I advised you

00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:54.400
to let it rest.

00:23:54.720 --> 00:23:55.759
You kept your silence.

00:23:56.680 --> 00:23:57.759
Now, Wang

00:23:57.759 --> 00:23:59.039
lies dead.

00:23:59.599 --> 00:24:00.920
Can you

00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:04.119
truly claim

00:24:05.400 --> 00:24:06.880
you had no hand in this?

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:16.640
My lord,

00:24:17.720 --> 00:24:20.319
I am unjustly accused.

00:24:20.799 --> 00:24:22.079
I kept silent because

00:24:22.359 --> 00:24:23.519
my bitterness

00:24:24.079 --> 00:24:25.680
was beyond words.

00:24:27.880 --> 00:24:29.599
What bitterness?

00:24:33.119 --> 00:24:34.240
I fail to understand.

00:24:34.799 --> 00:24:35.880
I laid the proof

00:24:36.119 --> 00:24:36.880
of Wang's

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:38.079
corruption

00:24:38.079 --> 00:24:39.119
before you.

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:40.839
Why do you

00:24:41.119 --> 00:24:42.279
defend him with such fervor?

00:24:54.200 --> 00:24:55.000
It seems

00:24:55.240 --> 00:24:56.759
Wang's words held truth after all.

00:24:57.519 --> 00:24:59.119
What did he say?

00:24:59.839 --> 00:25:01.000
After the bran scandal,

00:25:01.519 --> 00:25:02.680
Wang and I shared a drink.

00:25:03.559 --> 00:25:04.519
He boasted that

00:25:04.839 --> 00:25:06.720
he had done far more for you

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:08.519
than I ever did.

00:25:09.160 --> 00:25:10.079
That scheme

00:25:10.519 --> 00:25:11.359
to swap
grain for bran?

00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:13.720
It was your strategy

00:25:14.160 --> 00:25:15.839
to topple Fan Chuan!

00:25:18.799 --> 00:25:19.519
He pocketed

00:25:20.359 --> 00:25:23.000
the bribes

00:25:23.519 --> 00:25:24.880
for you,

00:25:25.400 --> 00:25:26.119
and you

00:25:26.519 --> 00:25:28.039
repaid his service

00:25:28.440 --> 00:25:30.440
with a prison cell.

00:25:32.759 --> 00:25:35.240
You bring tavern-talk

00:25:35.559 --> 00:25:38.039
in front of His Majesty?

00:25:38.039 --> 00:25:39.880
You have grown truly arrogant!

00:25:42.400 --> 00:25:44.240
Tavern-talk is unworthy of belief?

00:25:44.880 --> 00:25:45.559
Then

00:25:46.279 --> 00:25:47.680
by what right

00:25:47.880 --> 00:25:49.039
do you accuse me,

00:25:49.960 --> 00:25:51.960
based solely on a past grudge?

00:25:52.440 --> 00:25:54.680
You twist words like a snake!

00:26:00.799 --> 00:26:01.839
Lord Fang!

00:26:03.599 --> 00:26:04.559
Present, my lord.

00:26:06.680 --> 00:26:07.400
Lord Li!

00:26:11.920 --> 00:26:13.000
My lord.

00:26:13.759 --> 00:26:14.440
Lord Wen!

00:26:18.640 --> 00:26:19.359
At your service, my lord.

00:26:19.720 --> 00:26:20.680
I demand the Court of Judicial

00:26:20.680 --> 00:26:22.039
preside over this case.

00:26:22.720 --> 00:26:24.680
The Ministry of Justice and the Censorate shall assist.

00:26:25.319 --> 00:26:26.440
Chen's guilt

00:26:27.119 --> 00:26:28.440
is plain as day!

00:26:35.920 --> 00:26:36.680
Your Majesty!

00:26:37.200 --> 00:26:39.920
Lord Ye Xian requests an audience!

00:26:48.240 --> 00:26:48.799
Your Majesty,

00:26:49.440 --> 00:26:50.000
I have secured

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:51.519
the Wang manor

00:26:51.720 --> 00:26:53.039
and questioned all within.

00:26:53.519 --> 00:26:54.400
We have a significant lead.

00:26:56.519 --> 00:26:57.200
What is it?
Present it at once!

00:27:30.640 --> 00:27:31.440
Your Majesty...

00:28:11.039 --> 00:28:12.920
The session should be over.

00:28:14.200 --> 00:28:15.839
Where is him?

00:28:24.039 --> 00:28:26.359
The Chunyuan Sect?

00:28:27.079 --> 00:28:27.880
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:28:28.200 --> 00:28:29.680
This is their symbol,

00:28:30.400 --> 00:28:31.519
"The Fearless,"

00:28:32.039 --> 00:28:33.079
an oath of unwavering,

00:28:33.519 --> 00:28:34.319
fatal devotion.

00:28:35.680 --> 00:28:37.039
I found this very mark

00:28:37.039 --> 00:28:38.240
upon the Wangs' steward.

00:28:40.839 --> 00:28:42.359
But as I recall,

00:28:42.680 --> 00:28:44.200
they were crushed

00:28:44.200 --> 00:28:45.839
when the prince's coup failed.

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:47.519
They were

00:28:48.039 --> 00:28:49.079
meant to be eradicated!

00:28:49.680 --> 00:28:50.480
Your Majesty,

00:28:51.400 --> 00:28:52.279
though

00:28:52.920 --> 00:28:54.240
the majority were,

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:56.079
many fled to the north

00:28:56.759 --> 00:28:58.160
and took refuge

00:28:58.680 --> 00:29:01.000
with the barbarians.

00:29:01.599 --> 00:29:02.680
Unbelievable!

00:29:03.559 --> 00:29:04.160
Why would they

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:05.480
harbor such cultists?

00:29:05.839 --> 00:29:06.920
Many of those

00:29:07.359 --> 00:29:09.079
who fled were

00:29:09.359 --> 00:29:10.680
learned men,

00:29:11.519 --> 00:29:12.559
scholars

00:29:12.759 --> 00:29:14.559
of rank.

00:29:15.319 --> 00:29:15.960
The Northerners

00:29:16.319 --> 00:29:17.240
have

00:29:17.720 --> 00:29:19.559
co-opted them

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:20.880
into their service.

00:29:23.079 --> 00:29:24.680
Then why

00:29:24.680 --> 00:29:25.519
would Wang

00:29:25.519 --> 00:29:26.799
employ a Chunyuan fanatic?

00:29:27.279 --> 00:29:27.880
Your Majesty,

00:29:29.079 --> 00:29:30.119
they're merely

00:29:30.559 --> 00:29:31.920
a broken ghost

00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:34.119
of the past.

00:29:34.119 --> 00:29:35.319
A few desperate remnants

00:29:35.319 --> 00:29:36.160
that pose

00:29:36.359 --> 00:29:38.559
no danger

00:29:38.839 --> 00:29:40.160
to your throne.

00:29:40.759 --> 00:29:41.440
I advise

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:43.279
a discreet

00:29:43.519 --> 00:29:44.920
investigation.

00:29:45.400 --> 00:29:46.839
We must not let

00:29:47.599 --> 00:29:48.440
their whispers

00:29:48.759 --> 00:29:50.039
poison the minds

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:51.759
of the people.

00:29:52.960 --> 00:29:54.200
Wise words, my lord.

00:29:57.599 --> 00:29:58.359
And

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:00.880
what of Lord Chen?

00:30:19.400 --> 00:30:20.839
Let him to

00:30:21.559 --> 00:30:22.960
withdraw and recuperate.

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:24.599
Your Majesty,

00:30:25.839 --> 00:30:28.119
state affairs require my attention.

00:30:28.519 --> 00:30:29.519
I beg your leave.

00:30:30.799 --> 00:30:31.319
Um...

00:30:59.359 --> 00:31:00.240
What is it, my lord?

00:31:00.799 --> 00:31:01.920
Did you know

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:02.759
the Wangs' steward

00:31:02.759 --> 00:31:04.440
had the "Fearless" branded

00:31:04.440 --> 00:31:06.359
onto his own skin?

00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:11.279
Who told you such a thing?

00:31:12.079 --> 00:31:13.200
It was uncovered by Ye Xian.

00:31:14.400 --> 00:31:15.359
It cannot be!

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.640
Our sect teaches that

00:31:17.799 --> 00:31:19.240
our flesh must

00:31:19.519 --> 00:31:21.039
remain pristine.

00:31:21.519 --> 00:31:23.079
We do not mar our skin,

00:31:23.759 --> 00:31:25.000
let alone brand it

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:26.160
with our marks!

00:31:38.039 --> 00:31:39.400
Did someone stage it?

00:31:43.079 --> 00:31:43.720
Gods.

00:31:45.039 --> 00:31:45.839
We've been played!

00:31:47.599 --> 00:31:48.200
Ye Xian!

00:31:51.599 --> 00:31:52.079
My lord.

00:31:56.039 --> 00:31:56.680
You must be

00:31:57.160 --> 00:31:57.799
famished.
I brought meat pies.

00:32:00.880 --> 00:32:01.440
Not hungry.

00:32:02.640 --> 00:32:03.880
His Majesty has kept me.

00:32:05.319 --> 00:32:06.160
Leave.

00:32:07.200 --> 00:32:08.440
He kept you?

00:32:09.000 --> 00:32:09.839
A guard would

00:32:09.839 --> 00:32:11.119
have told us.

00:32:11.599 --> 00:32:12.960
But you came here yourself.

00:32:14.880 --> 00:32:16.279
Worried I'd lose sleep?

00:32:19.359 --> 00:32:20.160
I'm here

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:22.000
for Li Xianhuai.

00:32:24.319 --> 00:32:26.200
Right, yes...

00:32:29.119 --> 00:32:30.200
You and

00:32:30.680 --> 00:32:32.079
your pride!

00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:34.519
My lord!

00:32:36.119 --> 00:32:36.799
My love,

00:32:37.400 --> 00:32:38.240
all well?

00:32:40.359 --> 00:32:40.920
Rest easy.

00:32:41.799 --> 00:32:42.400
Why did you come?

00:32:43.160 --> 00:32:44.440
I could not remain home while

00:32:44.599 --> 00:32:45.359
you faced danger.

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:47.079
A man as crafty as he?

00:32:47.640 --> 00:32:48.839
Danger is his playground.

00:32:49.680 --> 00:32:50.319
Ye Xian,

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.160
must you always be

00:32:52.359 --> 00:32:53.119
so venomous?

00:32:55.240 --> 00:32:56.200
Then stop pulling him
into your games!

00:32:59.599 --> 00:33:00.559
Stay out of this!

00:33:01.000 --> 00:33:01.720
Why?

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:03.400
Every time they face ruin,

00:33:03.400 --> 00:33:04.519
you're the one caught in the fray!

00:33:09.920 --> 00:33:10.759
You're married!

00:33:11.359 --> 00:33:12.240
Can't you leave him

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:13.319
out of your schemes?

00:33:17.359 --> 00:33:17.880
Let's go home.

00:33:27.119 --> 00:33:27.640
See.

00:33:28.000 --> 00:33:29.400
Cat's got their tongues.

00:33:36.559 --> 00:33:37.240
Ruixiang,

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:39.319
why do I find that

00:33:39.319 --> 00:33:40.799
surly nature of his so charming?

00:33:41.880 --> 00:33:43.680
You have an eye for a rare soul.

00:33:56.319 --> 00:33:57.079
What is this?

00:33:58.720 --> 00:33:59.640
A message from Ye Xian.

00:34:00.039 --> 00:34:01.079
An audience

00:34:01.519 --> 00:34:02.440
with His Majesty.

00:34:08.760 --> 00:34:09.559
Greetings,

00:34:10.360 --> 00:34:11.719
Your Majesty.

00:34:13.440 --> 00:34:14.119
No formalities.

00:34:16.039 --> 00:34:16.920
Gratitude.

00:34:17.039 --> 00:34:17.960
Gratitude, Your Majesty.

00:34:22.199 --> 00:34:23.920
We meet again, my lady.

00:34:24.440 --> 00:34:25.599
You have a remarkable gift,

00:34:25.960 --> 00:34:27.239
making two of

00:34:27.239 --> 00:34:27.960
my finest lords

00:34:28.119 --> 00:34:29.400
jealous over you.

00:34:34.119 --> 00:34:34.800
Your Majesty,

00:34:35.159 --> 00:34:36.079
the streets

00:34:36.400 --> 00:34:37.719
are no place

00:34:38.199 --> 00:34:39.599
for a sovereign.

00:34:39.599 --> 00:34:40.800
You should return at once.

00:34:41.639 --> 00:34:43.000
Lord Chen speaks wisely.

00:34:43.360 --> 00:34:44.519
I shall escort you back.

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:46.039
Not yet!

00:34:46.519 --> 00:34:47.199
It took great effort

00:34:47.199 --> 00:34:48.719
to sneak out.

00:34:49.559 --> 00:34:50.800
Fine! I won't speak

00:34:50.800 --> 00:34:51.400
another word

00:34:52.039 --> 00:34:52.679
of

00:34:52.800 --> 00:34:53.719
your little triangle!

00:34:56.599 --> 00:34:57.519
You two, withdraw.

00:34:57.800 --> 00:34:58.800
I'll speak with Lord Chen alone.

00:35:00.440 --> 00:35:02.280
My gratitude for recalling Ye Xian.

00:35:02.559 --> 00:35:03.960
It was the only way

00:35:04.320 --> 00:35:05.960
to make Lord Fu yield.

00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:07.440
The credit is yours.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:09.880
Had you not

00:35:10.199 --> 00:35:11.360
traced

00:35:11.360 --> 00:35:12.360
that steward

00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:14.159
back to

00:35:14.800 --> 00:35:15.679
Lord Fu's recommendation,

00:35:15.679 --> 00:35:16.840
I would still

00:35:18.039 --> 00:35:19.400
be blind to

00:35:19.880 --> 00:35:20.880
my Chief Councilor's ties

00:35:21.199 --> 00:35:22.639
to the Chunyuan Sect.

00:35:23.079 --> 00:35:24.039
Perhaps there's

00:35:24.519 --> 00:35:25.519
a misunderstanding.

00:35:26.440 --> 00:35:27.760
Spare me his defense.

00:35:28.119 --> 00:35:29.719
A man as shrewd as him

00:35:30.039 --> 00:35:30.760
does not
recommend a man

00:35:31.519 --> 00:35:32.440
without knowing his origins.

00:35:33.440 --> 00:35:34.360
I believe

00:35:35.039 --> 00:35:35.840
he knew

00:35:36.119 --> 00:35:36.960
that steward's

00:35:36.960 --> 00:35:38.239
identity

00:35:38.519 --> 00:35:39.280
perfectly well.

00:35:42.719 --> 00:35:43.679
He's been

00:35:43.960 --> 00:35:45.400
a pillar of the empire,

00:35:45.960 --> 00:35:47.800
and I have honored that.

00:35:48.599 --> 00:35:50.239
But he overreaches,

00:35:50.599 --> 00:35:51.519
spinning his webs

00:35:51.679 --> 00:35:52.519
of influence

00:35:52.760 --> 00:35:53.519
as though

00:35:53.800 --> 00:35:54.800
the throne

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:55.719
were his to claim!

00:35:56.280 --> 00:35:57.039
Now,

00:35:57.039 --> 00:35:58.159
to find him

00:35:58.159 --> 00:35:58.960
conspired with cultists?

00:35:59.719 --> 00:36:00.320
He is surely

00:36:00.639 --> 00:36:02.039
plotting something far darker.

00:36:03.519 --> 00:36:04.119
I'm lucky

00:36:04.920 --> 00:36:06.760
to have you and Ye Xian,

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:07.519
men willing to
stake their lives for me.

00:36:10.679 --> 00:36:11.840
It is my duty, Your Majesty.

00:36:13.440 --> 00:36:14.599
I have no more titles

00:36:14.960 --> 00:36:16.440
to award Ye Xian for now;

00:36:16.920 --> 00:36:18.960
it must wait until I'm truly in command.

00:36:19.719 --> 00:36:20.519
But you,

00:36:21.360 --> 00:36:23.000
I have spoken with Mother.

00:36:23.840 --> 00:36:25.719
You shall be elevated.

00:36:26.159 --> 00:36:26.719
Your Majesty...

00:36:26.719 --> 00:36:27.840
She has consented.

00:36:28.280 --> 00:36:29.039
With her approval,

00:36:29.599 --> 00:36:31.000
Lord Fu has no grounds to protest.

00:36:33.920 --> 00:36:34.840
I accept it

00:36:35.880 --> 00:36:38.159
with all humility, Your Majesty.

00:36:38.599 --> 00:36:40.400
Get well.

00:36:40.840 --> 00:36:43.039
I need you

00:36:43.639 --> 00:36:44.760
fighting-fit

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:46.199
for the battles ahead.

00:36:47.880 --> 00:36:49.440
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:36:51.000 --> 00:36:51.880
I never imagined

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:54.280
the Emperor would reach out to you.

00:37:02.639 --> 00:37:03.920
Without him,

00:37:04.639 --> 00:37:05.320
I'd have to

00:37:05.320 --> 00:37:06.760
bide my time for years

00:37:07.320 --> 00:37:08.639
before I could challenge Lord Fu.

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:10.719
And without Ye Xian and me,

00:37:10.719 --> 00:37:11.519
His Majesty

00:37:11.760 --> 00:37:12.800
would never seize true power.

00:37:13.360 --> 00:37:14.159
It is

00:37:16.199 --> 00:37:17.079
a strange destiny.

00:37:19.960 --> 00:37:21.639
But mark my words:

00:37:23.440 --> 00:37:24.519
our sovereign is

00:37:25.599 --> 00:37:26.400
coming into his own.

00:37:27.599 --> 00:37:28.519
What if

00:37:29.719 --> 00:37:31.800
Fu Hailian suspects

00:37:32.639 --> 00:37:34.159
the mark

00:37:34.639 --> 00:37:35.800
was

00:37:36.159 --> 00:37:37.000
your handiwork?

00:37:37.280 --> 00:37:37.920
It is possible.

00:37:40.039 --> 00:37:41.440
But it changes nothing.

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:42.519
The tie between us

00:37:42.920 --> 00:37:43.360
is severed;

00:37:43.360 --> 00:37:44.800
there is no going back.

00:37:45.320 --> 00:37:46.519
But if

00:37:47.159 --> 00:37:48.360
the sect

00:37:48.800 --> 00:37:50.119
is truly at his command,

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:53.199
he will never stop hunting you.

00:37:53.559 --> 00:37:54.920
Precisely why

00:37:55.639 --> 00:37:56.800
I must drag

00:37:57.280 --> 00:37:58.400
this conflict

00:37:58.400 --> 00:38:00.079
into the light.

00:38:01.079 --> 00:38:02.039
Better to face him
in the open

00:38:03.599 --> 00:38:04.199
than to

00:38:05.239 --> 00:38:06.880
have him plotting

00:38:07.119 --> 00:38:08.400
in the shadows.

00:38:10.960 --> 00:38:12.280
My hands are tied.

00:38:13.280 --> 00:38:14.800
His eyes

00:38:15.239 --> 00:38:16.039
are everywhere.

00:38:17.679 --> 00:38:18.519
I'm sending

00:38:18.960 --> 00:38:21.000
Qingpu to Shanxi.

00:38:23.519 --> 00:38:24.639
Those cultists

00:38:24.800 --> 00:38:26.199
fled north,

00:38:27.000 --> 00:38:28.679
which borders Shanxi.

00:38:29.320 --> 00:38:30.559
I've long had trade

00:38:30.559 --> 00:38:31.719
established there.

00:38:32.599 --> 00:38:33.360
I'll send her
under the cover

00:38:34.199 --> 00:38:35.239
of managing my trade,

00:38:35.800 --> 00:38:36.440
but she

00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:37.880
will be tracking

00:38:37.880 --> 00:38:39.039
the sect's shadow.

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:40.519
She is
as skilled

00:38:41.880 --> 00:38:42.519
as she is discreet.

00:38:43.239 --> 00:38:43.800
What do you think?

00:38:44.360 --> 00:38:45.519
A clever gambit, truly.

00:38:53.840 --> 00:38:55.320
Take your time.

00:38:55.639 --> 00:38:56.440
I have work to attend to.
Of course.

00:39:04.519 --> 00:39:05.599
[I've been to the border markets]

00:39:05.599 --> 00:39:06.519
[twice.]

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:08.800
[I've spotted a barbarian merchant]

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:10.079
[keeping a Yan translator]

00:39:10.559 --> 00:39:11.800
[who reeks of secrets.]

00:39:12.320 --> 00:39:13.400
[He performs rites daily;]

00:39:13.559 --> 00:39:15.039
[when I pressed him on his faith,]

00:39:15.039 --> 00:39:16.000
[he turned evasive.]

00:39:16.599 --> 00:39:17.800
[As you instructed,]

00:39:18.000 --> 00:39:19.119
[I have kept my distance.]

00:39:28.239 --> 00:39:29.440
Wang Nianen was

00:39:29.440 --> 00:39:31.079
introduced to Wang Xuanfan

00:39:31.519 --> 00:39:33.079
by Fu Hailian himself.

00:39:33.519 --> 00:39:34.320
I've followed that trail

00:39:34.320 --> 00:39:35.400
to the end,

00:39:36.360 --> 00:39:37.559
yet I have found

00:39:38.039 --> 00:39:39.079
nothing.

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:40.519
The Chunyuan Sect is

00:39:40.519 --> 00:39:41.519
crawling all over this city.

00:39:42.000 --> 00:39:43.519
They are far from subtle.

00:39:44.320 --> 00:39:45.639
He is a low-level lackey;

00:39:45.639 --> 00:39:47.039
how could he

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:48.519
possibly

00:39:48.519 --> 00:39:49.920
vanish from your sight?

00:39:50.079 --> 00:39:51.519
You should have

00:39:52.199 --> 00:39:53.280
found something by now.

00:39:53.280 --> 00:39:54.360
Why are your hands empty?

00:39:55.159 --> 00:39:56.360
Are you suggesting

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:57.840
someone is obstructing us?

00:39:58.599 --> 00:39:59.920
But Wang Xuanfan is dead.

00:40:01.159 --> 00:40:02.320
Could it be Fu Hailian?

00:40:03.119 --> 00:40:04.000
We shall see.

00:40:06.320 --> 00:40:07.360
But you already

00:40:07.639 --> 00:40:08.800
suspect him, right?

00:40:10.119 --> 00:40:10.960
Fu is

00:40:11.239 --> 00:40:12.760
too sharp to

00:40:13.199 --> 00:40:13.880
let a man of

00:40:13.880 --> 00:40:14.960
unknown origins

00:40:15.199 --> 00:40:16.639
into Wang's house.

00:40:18.039 --> 00:40:18.960
He must have known

00:40:18.960 --> 00:40:20.679
Wang Nianen was a cultist.

00:40:21.320 --> 00:40:22.280
But then,

00:40:22.599 --> 00:40:23.719
if he knew,

00:40:23.719 --> 00:40:24.719
why

00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:25.920
place him there

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:27.039
for all these years?

00:40:27.039 --> 00:40:27.760
It seems

00:40:28.639 --> 00:40:29.679
Fu is inextricably

00:40:29.679 --> 00:40:31.119
bound to the sect.

00:40:31.280 --> 00:40:32.239
Those are theories,

00:40:32.960 --> 00:40:33.920
not facts.

00:40:34.639 --> 00:40:36.320
My men are under surveillance;

00:40:36.440 --> 00:40:37.880
I can't make a move.

00:40:38.679 --> 00:40:39.639
I must rely on you.

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:44.840
So, you're finally begging me?

00:40:45.960 --> 00:40:46.920
Beg? Not at all.

00:40:47.639 --> 00:40:48.639
Feel free to quit.

00:40:52.360 --> 00:40:53.079
You know,

00:40:53.679 --> 00:40:55.320
the one I truly wish to investigate

00:40:56.320 --> 00:40:57.039
is you.

00:40:59.400 --> 00:41:00.519
You seem to know

00:41:01.119 --> 00:41:02.360
every detail

00:41:02.679 --> 00:41:03.400
of the sect;

00:41:04.079 --> 00:41:04.920
how are you so well-versed

00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:06.960
in their darkness?

00:41:07.880 --> 00:41:08.800
Maybe

00:41:09.679 --> 00:41:11.159
read a book once in a while.

00:41:11.679 --> 00:41:12.920
I'm starting to think

00:41:13.960 --> 00:41:15.320
you're one of them.

00:41:15.840 --> 00:41:17.440
By all means,

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:18.519
investigate me then.

00:41:21.039 --> 00:41:22.159
Don't tempt me.

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:34.960
His Majesty sent word.

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:36.360
He Wenxin's away on leave.

00:41:37.000 --> 00:41:38.559
Fu is officially pinning

00:41:38.559 --> 00:41:40.400
the Wangs' murders on the sect.

00:41:42.000 --> 00:41:42.920
Even the attempt on your life

00:41:44.119 --> 00:41:44.920
is conveniently pinned
on Wang Xuanfan.

00:41:46.639 --> 00:41:47.719
To cross you,

00:41:48.000 --> 00:41:48.519
Wang Xuanfan truly

00:41:48.519 --> 00:41:49.559
invited his own doom.

00:41:52.440 --> 00:41:52.960
My lord,

00:41:53.840 --> 00:41:54.440
the royal messenger is here.

00:41:57.239 --> 00:41:57.880
Ah, the decree

00:41:57.880 --> 00:41:59.519
for your promotion

00:41:59.519 --> 00:42:00.159
is finally here.

00:42:00.559 --> 00:42:01.480
My congratulations!

00:42:01.840 --> 00:42:02.880
I suppose His Majesty's plan

00:42:02.880 --> 00:42:04.360
to break Fu's grip

00:42:04.639 --> 00:42:05.719
rests on your shoulders now.

00:42:09.880 --> 00:42:11.039
Mercy or lash,

00:42:11.559 --> 00:42:12.800
all is grace from the throne.

00:42:13.840 --> 00:42:16.760
By Imperial Decree:

00:42:17.079 --> 00:42:18.679
Chen Yanyun, for his

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:20.960
unwavering loyalty

00:42:21.239 --> 00:42:22.639
and

00:42:22.639 --> 00:42:24.000
exceptional governance,

00:42:24.239 --> 00:42:25.639
is promoted to

00:42:25.639 --> 00:42:27.119
Senior Grand Secretary

00:42:27.360 --> 00:42:30.159
and named

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:32.320
Guardian of the Crown Prince.

00:42:32.719 --> 00:42:34.039
So it is decreed.

00:42:34.840 --> 00:42:37.239
I am humbled by this honor.

00:42:37.840 --> 00:42:41.239
Long live the Emperor!

00:42:43.559 --> 00:42:45.519
Our trade bureaus,

00:42:46.000 --> 00:42:47.320
shipyards

00:42:47.840 --> 00:42:49.079
and the weaving bureaus

00:42:49.639 --> 00:42:51.280
are all in dire need of funds.

00:42:51.920 --> 00:42:53.119
The cabinet has agreed

00:42:53.400 --> 00:42:54.559
to divert

00:42:54.880 --> 00:42:56.199
thirty percent

00:42:56.320 --> 00:42:57.280
of our frontier defense funding

00:42:57.800 --> 00:42:59.519
to bolster these institutions.

00:43:01.199 --> 00:43:03.559
If the cabinet has reached

00:43:04.320 --> 00:43:05.320
a consensus...
Your Majesty,

00:43:06.320 --> 00:43:08.199
I must object.

00:43:22.199 --> 00:43:23.599
Lord Fu is pushing to

00:43:24.079 --> 00:43:25.679
cut frontier defense budget,

00:43:25.679 --> 00:43:26.599
despite the opposition.

00:43:27.000 --> 00:43:27.880
We have been

00:43:28.239 --> 00:43:29.280
locked in war

00:43:29.719 --> 00:43:30.559
with the barbarians
for two decades;

00:43:32.079 --> 00:43:33.760
the truce is barely a year old.

00:43:34.639 --> 00:43:36.119
By what right does he

00:43:36.880 --> 00:43:38.760
gamble with our borders?

00:43:39.679 --> 00:43:41.519
Unless he knows,

00:43:41.519 --> 00:43:42.960
with absolute certainty,

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:44.400
that they won't invade us.

00:43:46.400 --> 00:43:48.000
How could he be certain?

00:43:51.920 --> 00:43:53.039
There is but one answer:

00:43:53.719 --> 00:43:54.760
he has eyes

00:43:54.920 --> 00:43:56.320
within the enemy's ranks,

00:43:56.800 --> 00:43:58.239
a network unknown

00:43:59.920 --> 00:44:00.840
to our generals

00:44:01.440 --> 00:44:02.239
the court,

00:44:03.159 --> 00:44:04.639
or even His Majesty.

00:44:06.280 --> 00:44:06.920
Which makes them

00:44:06.920 --> 00:44:08.519
his own private hounds.

00:44:10.000 --> 00:44:11.519
I'm going to see His Majesty!

00:44:12.920 --> 00:44:13.599
Choose a more

00:44:13.599 --> 00:44:14.679
discreet place next time.

00:44:15.119 --> 00:44:15.840
Fear not.

00:44:16.039 --> 00:44:16.920
I shall be as a shadow.